  "description": "OpenTelemetry Collector self-observability. The collector exposes its own metrics on :8888/metrics; the prometheus/self receiver inside the same process scrapes them every 15s and ships them through the OTLP -> clickhouseexporter pipeline alongside everything else. Metric prefix is otelcol_*; service.name=otelcol.",
